{"tid":1771774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"淘大商場有人聚集並一度與保安爭執","createTime":"2019-12-06T05:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:01:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"983814e4dab64ab7be820184244361afdfe6a8f0","tid":1771774,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tnvzoRiIkLn2FHHMwQhakQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/SING-KLE-191205-22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtnvzoRiIkLn2FHHMwQhakQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FSING-KLE-191205-22.jpg&h=2ec176f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】九龍灣淘大商場晚上有人聚集，保安人員一度鎖上商場部分出入口，與聚集人士發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n數十名戴上口罩的人士在商場中庭的各樓層聚集，他們高叫口號並唱反修例歌曲，部分商店提早關門，包括多次在反修例示威中被破壞的一間連鎖快餐店。<br />\n<br />\n約八時許，商場部分出入口提早上鎖並落下捲閘，引起在場人士不滿並與保安人員理論，有人用手提電話照向保安，雙方有輕微推撞，有人就打破消防警鐘，警鐘一度響起，最後保安員重新開放出入口。"},{"pid":"cf63d9496daa731e49df61443d1e5c42b7e3c5d2","tid":1771774,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"最後保安員重新開放出入口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e3ad971053e42f9a2d5971e1a35ef287822007","tid":1771774,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2jgKehQuSYdgXtTcyg8g7A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/fa49e4d6e2a055a7828915ea64fa9938\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2jgKehQuSYdgXtTcyg8g7A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ffa49e4d6e2a055a7828915ea64fa9938&h=3f042e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有網民發起反修例活動。昨晚在九龍灣淘大商場中庭發起的「東九龍和你唱」活動，一度有近百人聚集唱歌，多間商店需提早關門落閘。<br />\n<br />\n商場管理公司大為緊張，在活動開始前一個多小時，已將商場兩個近中庭出入口封閉，並派出近十名保安員在附近監察，此舉惹來唱歌人士不滿，一度包圍保安質問，保安遂把門打開，最終和平解決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rAItpcej_20AnDMRO7Pu9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/f14494e0348cb5f0b3dafb5d474f1565\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrAItpcej_20AnDMRO7Pu9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ff14494e0348cb5f0b3dafb5d474f1565&h=b182ef88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚近八時，有人站在淘大商場二樓及三樓的玻璃圍欄，開始大喊「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號，並高唱《願榮光歸香港》，揭開活動序幕。不少身穿黑衣、戴口罩人士加入，現場一度聚集近百人。不少商店提早關門，包括早前屢成為攻擊目標的吉野家及元氣壽司；但仍有商場顧客未受影響，依然繼續行街購物。<br />\n<br />\n由於商場管理公司提早關閉兩個出入口，惹來唱歌人士不滿，一度有多名唱歌人士圍着追問在場的保安員，並指商場有可能違反消防條例，場面一度有些混亂，事件擾攘十多分鐘，最後保安員妥協重新開門，人群其後和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n此外，一連多日的「和你lunch」活動昨日仍持續，中環及葵涌繼續有人於午飯時段聚集，其中在中環約有二百人舉起標語及築成人鏈，表達訴求；葵涌亦有二百人聚集，並由九龍貿易中心出發，途徑葵昌路、大連排道遊行，沿途叫口號。"},{"pid":"e7c613fe75277aba5d86daa539fdb57cc5dab9b4","tid":1771774,"uid":64743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"之前個有班大陸藍絲入黎搞事<br />\n果晚個保安比人屌到爆點解唔封門<br />\nE+明玩野<br />\n居民你都封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1cc466ccfa0f07cc3a91c5b163f290e473fb22","tid":1771774,"uid":76148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128f739161e8de8acf58d43b5eabe8e4dc74efca","tid":1771774,"uid":34616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾商場垃圾保安"},{"pid":"b5f2ba07bef457ec6c37d3e3531dd064e1d79248","tid":1771774,"uid":227813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}